OL,6,     FCortina/Austin Campervan: As a
OL,7,     Fteenager, all Dave wanted for his
OL,8,     Ffirst car was a 2 litre Ghia
OL,9,     FCortina, and today he's off to
OL,10,     FNottinghamshire to collect just
OL,11,     Fthat, alongside a Mark 1 Capri.
OL,12,G0000 Bangers & Cash
OL,13,     FAston DB4/Tractor: Derek heads off
OL,14,     Fto Colchester to pick up a 1960
OL,15,     FAston Martin DB4 that has been
OL,16,     Fsitting under a tarpaulin in a
OL,17,     Fgarage that has collapsed round it
OL,18,     Ffor 40 years.
